## agGridAlpineFontFace variable

The AG Alpine font face used on ag-theme-alpine/ag-theme-alpine-dark Grid Pro themes.

**Signature:**

```typescript
agGridAlpineFontFace = "\n  @font-face {\n    font-family: \"agGridAlpine\";\n    src: url(data:font/woff2;charset=utf-8;base64,);\n    font-weight: normal;\n    font-style: normal;\n  }\n"
```
